There is a place called KGF, ruled by a cruel person who was rude to his workers. 
He had set up a trapdoor so his workers could not go outside.
The workers were there to mine gold which was sold by the ruler.
Rocky was assigned to kill the ruler of KGF.
Rocky makes plans and enters KGF and crosses the white line beyond
which the ruler lives.
He enters the house of the ruler and kills his younger brother.
Ruler kills two of the caged assassinators in his house.
Rocky pretends to be the third caged one and beheads the ruler.